knowledgeGraph.title: UCSF Bakar Cancer Hospital
knowledgeGraph.type: Cancer treatment center in San Francisco, California
knowledgeGraph.description: UCSF Bakar Cancer Hospital is a cancer hospital in San Francisco, California, part of the University of California, San Francisco health system. It is part of the UCSF Medical Center campus of Mission Bay. Opened on February 1, 2015, part of a $1.5 billion project.
